sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>DashboardPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>DashboardStatsView
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to Dashboard
    FE->>API: GET /api/alerts/dashboard-stats/
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.count()
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(severity="critical").count()
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.values("alert_type").annotate(Count)
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.values("protocol").annotate(Count)
    API->>DB: BlockedIP.objects.count()
    DB-->>API: Aggregated statistics
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {total_alerts, by_severity, by_type, by_protocol, blocked_count}
    FE->>FE: StatCard(stats)
    FE->>FE: RiskGauge(risk_score)
    FE->>FE: SeverityBar(severity_data)
    FE-->>U: Render dashboard with charts and statistics
